	(text_box "To-add:\n- Bootstrap Caps (BOOTx to OUTx)\n- (Local) Bus Decoupling Caps\n- Current Shunts (Internal Op Amps + ADC), unliuke SPx/SNx\n\n- VCC Bypass Caoacutir -> CONTROL STAGE\n- Bus Voltage Sensing (ADC Input, ST shows example) -> CONTROL STAGE\n- Protection for MOSFET Faults (SCREF for VDS protection?) -> CONSTROL STAGE"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
